Laguna Heights first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[1990 U.S. census]].<ref name=1990CensusTX/> It is part of the [[Brownsville, Texas|Brownsville]]&ndash;[[Harlingen, Texas|Harlingen]] [[Brownsville-Harlingen metropolitan area|Metropolitan Statistical Area]].

